(() => {
  switch (type) {
    case "input":
      return [
        "-",
        "textarea",
        "text",
        "money",
        "number",
        "phone",
        "mask",
        "rich-text",
        "upload",
        "password",
        "datetime",
        "date",
        "time",
        "toggle",
        "import",
        "monthly",
        "key-value",
        "search",
        "otp",
      ];
    case "link":
      return ["-"];
    case "date":
      return ["-", "datetime", "date", "time"];
    case "single-option":
      return ["-", "dropdown", "radio", "toggle", "button", "checkbox"];
    case "multi-option":
      return [
        "-",
        "typeahead",
        "checkbox",
        "button",
        "table-edit",
        "table-list-edit",
      ];
  }
  return [];
})()
